title: Way Too Early 2023 Mock Draft
description:
Laura, Todd, Diana, Louis, and Hasselbeck discuss Daniel Jones’ 5th year option not being picked up, Jalen Hurts’ comments on his current situation, which teams had the best offseason, which teams didn’t do enough, and Todd’s way too early 2023 mock draft.
